text: Chor Machaye Shor () is a Pakistani Urdu movie. It was directed by Syed Noor. The movie stars Babar Ali, Resham and Sahiba. The movie was released in 1996. It is a remake of Punjabi movie Sohra te Jawai ==References== Category:1990s Pakistani movies Category:1996 movies
title: Chor Machaye Shor (1996 movie)
